Python Guitar Transcription Aid
===============================

This is a python program that helps transcribing guitar music by drawing the spectrum onto a fretboard. It currently is in a very early development state.

Requirements (Ubuntu)
---------------------

python
python-matplotlib
python-gtk2
python-pygoocanvas
python-gst0.10
python-gst0.10-dev
gstreamer0.10-plugins-bad
build-essentials
python-gobject
python-scipy
python-cairo

Building
--------

cd VisualizerControlBase
python setup.py build --build-lib=..

Running
-------

python transcribe.py
